      <item>
        <title>Half-Life 2 glowing gun sights</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Ramirezoid]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Open the texture file of the sight, create a new layer and fill it with black. Paint white areas where you want the model to glow(the white-marked part<br>
of the texture will glow). Delete the texture layer and save it as a vtf. This will be your glow texture.</p>
<p>In the VMT for the sight’s actual texture:</p>
<p>“$selfillum” 1<br>
“$normalmapalphaenvmapmask” 1<br>
“$selfillumtint” “[3 3 3]”<br>
“$selfillummask” “file path of glow texture goes here”</p>
          <p><a href="https://leakfree.org/t/half-life-2-glowing-gun-sights/4790/2">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
